delete.error-message:
There was an issue deleting your user data. Don't worry, this incident is being tracked and has been converted into a manual data deletion request (as opposed to an automatic one). Your data will be deleted within 30 days.

If you want, you may join the [support server]({{url}}) and request to see the status of your data deletion request.

about.description:
### Description

Welcome to the lovely Discord application for [Sky: Children of the Light]({{url}} "thatskygame")!

So you'd like to know about me, huh? Well, I like long walks across the Sanctuary Islands. Oh, and don't forget about gliding all over the Starlight Desert. Also... JELLYFISH!

Check out these useful links:
about.sponsor:
### Sponsoring

Want to give support? There are ways you can do that! Thank you in advance!

- [GitHub]({{githubSponsorsURL}})
